{
  "id": "adv_bond_suz_01_01",
  "title": "成宮すず1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ーーーっ！　怜の席はどこですの！\n大変ですの！　早くしないと間に合いませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Reiーーー! Where is Rei's seat!\nI'm in trouble! If don't hurry‚ I might be late!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 166.66666669999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 10.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すーずーっ！　私の教室で大きな声を出さないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suーzuー! Don't speak loudly in my classroom!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 166.6666667000012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "何回言ったら分かるのよ……すずの声、響くんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How many times do I have to tell you… Suzu's voice‚ is so loud",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 22.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そうは言いますけど……\n今の怜の声も同じくらい大きかったですわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said so‚ but…\nRei's voice was similarly loud?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "見てごらんなさいまし。ふふっ……ふふふっ……\nクラスメイトのみなさんも怜を見て笑っていますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please take a look. Hehe… hehehe…\nAll of your classmates are laughing at you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.56667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……！？　わ、私を見て笑ってるんじゃなくて\nすずを見て笑ってるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What…!? T-They're not laughing at me\nThey're laughing at Suzu!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.36667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ところで、急いでいたみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ you seem to be in a hurry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 44.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "何か用事があったんじゃないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn't you have something to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 50.23333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしたわ！　忘れていましたわ！\n怜、体操服を貸してくださいませんこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I did! I forgot!\nRei‚ could you please lend me your gym clothes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "え、嫌よ。無理",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ no. Impossible",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 57.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "意地が悪いですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're grumpy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 60.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "可愛い後輩がこんなにお願いしているというのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though your cute younger friend is asking you for so much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はあ……そもそも私とすずじゃサイズが違うでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… In the first place‚ Suzu and I are different sizes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "こころに借りなさいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Borrow from Kokoro",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それこそ無理ですわ！　体育祭の練習で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's impossible! Next class is a joint practice",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "次の時間は中等部全学年合同なんですの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for the sports day for all middle school students!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3200808929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "高等部も体育祭前だから、午前中に体育があったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "High school also had a sports day right before‚ so we had P.E all morning",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "だから私が一度着た体操服しかないし、無理",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I only have gym clothes that I've worn once‚ so it's impossible",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は気にしませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't care!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 94.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "怜の使ったものでも全然大丈夫ですわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Ray used it‚ it's totally fine‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "すずが気にしなくても私が気にするのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if Suzu doesn't care‚ I do!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 100.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それでは私は……どうやって体育に参加すれば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I…… how do I participate",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 104.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in P.E?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！？　まさか、サボれと言うんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh!? Are you telling me to skip it…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 111.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "あーもー分かったわよ！\n貸してあげるから静かにして！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohー‚ myー‚ I get it!\nI'll lend it to you‚ so be quiet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 116.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、こっち来て\n髪もそのままだと動きにくいでしょ。結んであげるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ come here\nIt's hard to move your hair like that. I'll tie it up",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 122.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 129.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとうございます。なんだかんだ怜は優しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Rei is kind anyway",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
